						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="article" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/CARIBBEANTALES-2012-FILM-Festival-10-15-April-2012-and-Caribbean-Young-Professionals-in-Science" title="CARIBBEANTALES 2012 FILM Festival 10-15 April 2012 and Caribbean Young Professionals in Science" alt="article">CARIBBEANTALES 2012 FILM Festival 10-15 April 2012 and Caribbean Young Professionals in Science</a></h2>

	
	
	
	
					<p>CTA is collaborating with CaribbeanTales Worldwide Distribution and CCST to showcase the winning videos of the CTA/CCST/CARDI/UWI Caribbean-wide Young Professionals in Agriculture and Science Film competitions during the CaribbeanTales 2012 Film Festival 10-15 April 2012, in Barbados.Vincent Lewis and Maliaka Brookes, 1st and 3rd place winners will represent all the finalists. On April 10, 2012 all the winning videos will be featured in a session which is dedicated to young people. The two winners will participate in a series of workshops for filmmakers and film fans that can best be described as a smorgasbord for filmmakers. The workshops are part of the CARIBBEANTALES Incubator Series. The activities will help film/television professionals develop world-class content by honing their skills in the continuum from script development to distribution. It will also contribute to raising the profile on the link between agriculture and science. Learn more about the winners who will attend the festival.</p>
							<p><span class="date">5/04/2012</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="article" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/CARIBBEANTALES-2012-FILM-Festival-10-15-April-2012-and-Caribbean-Young-Professionals-in-Science">Read more...</a>
